	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi I try to patch  NWCS to PAL by replaceing the PRG of every Game with a Hacked Pal version of it. i fixed Rad Racer since it had graphical issues. So Rad Racer is now fully playable on PAL consoles. Also i fixed Tetris to Pal with some glitches but I have problems with Super Mario Bros. .  I am not a programmer so every help would be welcome.<br /><br /><br />Here are some Infos. <br /><br />Nintendo World Championship 1990<br /><br /><br />Super Mario Bros.  	<br />---------------------------------------<br /><br />Offset:0x8010-0x1000F<br /><br /><br />Super Mario Bros. (E) [!].prg -	European PRG<br />Super Mario Bros. (U) [!].prg - US PRG<br />Super Mario Bros. (U) [WCS].prg - US World Championship PRG<br /><br />Rad Racer<br />---------------------------------------<br /><br />Offset:0x20010-0x4000F<br /><br /><br />Rad Racer (E) [!].prg -	European PRG<br />Rad Racer (U) [!].prg - US PRG<br />Rad Racer (U) [WCS].prg - US World Championship PRG<br />Rad Racer (E) [WCS].prg - US World Championship PRG patched with &quot;Rad Racer (E) [!].ips&quot;<br />Rad Racer (E) [!].ips - IPS Patch from &quot;Rad Racer (U) [!].prg&quot; to &quot;Rad Racer (E) [!].prg&quot;<br /><br /><br /><br />Tetris<br />---------------------------------------<br /><br />Offset:0x10010-0x1800F<br /><br /><br />Tetris (E) [!].prg -	European PRG<br />Tetris (U) [!].prg - US PRG<br />Tetris (U) [WCS].prg - US World Championship PRG<br />Tetris (E) [WCS].prg - US World Championship PRG patched with &quot;Tetris (U) [WCS].ips&quot;<br />Tetris (U) [WCS].ips - IPS Patch from &quot;Tetris (U) [!].prg&quot; to &quot;Tetris (U) [WSC].prg&quot;

		
